  "content": [
    "<span class='vocab-word' data-id='1'>Pagi</span> ini, <span class='vocab-word' data-id='2'>saya</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='3'>bangun</span> dengan perasaan <span class='vocab-word' data-id='4'>bagus</span>. <span class='vocab-word' data-id='5'>Saya</span> tidak <span class='vocab-word' data-id='6'>lelah</span>. <span class='vocab-word' data-id='7'>Apa</span> yang <span class='vocab-word' data-id='8'>saya</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='9'>ingin</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='10'>lakukan</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='11'>hari</span> ini? <span class='vocab-word' data-id='12'>Saya</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='13'>ingin</span> liburan <span class='vocab-word' data-id='14'>santai</span>!",
    
    "<span class='vocab-word' data-id='15'>Saya</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='16'>keluar</span> dari <span class='vocab-word' data-id='17'>kamar</span> dan <span class='vocab-word' data-id='18'>berjalan</span> ke <span class='vocab-word' data-id='19'>dapur</span>. <span class='vocab-word' data-id='20'>Saya</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='21'>buka</span> lemari dan <span class='vocab-word' data-id='22'>makan</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='23'>nasi goreng</span>. Mmm, sangat <span class='vocab-word' data-id='24'>enak</span>! <span class='vocab-word' data-id='25'>Lalu</span>, <span class='vocab-word' data-id='26'>saya</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='27'>minum</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='28'>secangkir</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='29'>kopi</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='30'>panas</span>.",
    
    "<span class='vocab-word' data-id='31'>Tiba-tiba</span>, ada <span class='vocab-word' data-id='32'>panggilan</span> dari <span class='vocab-word' data-id='33'>teman</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='34'>saya</span>. <span class='vocab-word' data-id='35'>Dia</span> bertanya, \"<span class='vocab-word' data-id='36'>Kamu</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='37'>ingin</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='38'>pergi</span> ke kafe <span class='vocab-word' data-id='39'>bersama</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='40'>kami</span>?\" <span class='vocab-word' data-id='41'>Saya</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='42'>tertawa</span> dan berkata, \"<span class='vocab-word' data-id='43'>Ya</span>! <span class='vocab-word' data-id='44'>Saya</span> tidak <span class='vocab-word' data-id='45'>terburu-buru</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='46'>hari</span> ini!\"",
    
    "<span class='vocab-word' data-id='47'>Saya</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='48'>masuk</span> ke <span class='vocab-word' data-id='49'>kamar</span> dan <span class='vocab-word' data-id='50'>buka</span> lemari. <span class='vocab-word' data-id='51'>Apa</span> yang <span class='vocab-word' data-id='52'>saya</span> pakai? <span class='vocab-word' data-id='53'>Lalu</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='54'>saya</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='55'>keluar</span> dari <span class='vocab-word' data-id='56'>rumah</span>. <span class='vocab-word' data-id='57'>Waktu</span> menunjukkan jam 10 <span class='vocab-word' data-id='58'>pagi</span>. Cuaca <span class='vocab-word' data-id='59'>panas</span>, <span class='vocab-word' data-id='60'>tapi</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='61'>saya</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='62'>suka</span>!",
    
    "<span class='vocab-word' data-id='63'>Saya</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='64'>berjalan</span> ke halte bus. <span class='vocab-word' data-id='65'>Di mana</span> kafe itu? Ah, tidak <span class='vocab-word' data-id='66'>jauh</span> dari <span class='vocab-word' data-id='67'>sini</span>. <span class='vocab-word' data-id='68'>Saat</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='69'>saya</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='70'>berjalan</span>, <span class='vocab-word' data-id='71'>saya</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='72'>lihat</span> banyak orang. <span class='vocab-word' data-id='73'>Mereka</span> juga <span class='vocab-word' data-id='74'>berjalan</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='75'>tanpa</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='76'>ragu</span>. Jakarta <span class='vocab-word' data-id='77'>selalu</span> ramai!",
    
    "<span class='vocab-word' data-id='78'>Saya</span> sampai di kafe. <span class='vocab-word' data-id='79'>Pemilik</span> kafe sangat <span class='vocab-word' data-id='80'>ramah</span>. <span class='vocab-word' data-id='81'>Dia</span> berkata, \"Selamat datang! <span class='vocab-word' data-id='82'>Tolong</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='83'>duduk</span> di <span class='vocab-word' data-id='84'>sini</span>.\" <span class='vocab-word' data-id='85'>Teman</span>-<span class='vocab-word' data-id='86'>teman</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='87'>saya</span> sudah <span class='vocab-word' data-id='88'>ada</span>. <span class='vocab-word' data-id='89'>Kami</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='90'>tertawa</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='91'>bersama</span>.",
    
    "\"<span class='vocab-word' data-id='92'>Apa kabar</span>?\" tanya <span class='vocab-word' data-id='93'>teman</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='94'>saya</span>. \"<span class='vocab-word' data-id='95'>Bagus</span>!\" jawab <span class='vocab-word' data-id='96'>saya</span>. <span class='vocab-word' data-id='97'>Kami</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='98'>minum</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='99'>kopi</span> dan <span class='vocab-word' data-id='100'>bicara</span> tentang <span class='vocab-word' data-id='101'>musik</span>. Ada <span class='vocab-word' data-id='102'>lagu</span> indie yang <span class='vocab-word' data-id='103'>enak</span>. <span class='vocab-word' data-id='104'>Kami</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='105'>menikmati</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='106'>waktu</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='107'>bersama</span>.",
    
    "<span class='vocab-word' data-id='108'>Saat</span> jam <span class='vocab-word' data-id='109'>satu</span>, <span class='vocab-word' data-id='110'>kami</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='111'>ingin</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='112'>makan</span>. <span class='vocab-word' data-id='113'>Apa</span> yang <span class='vocab-word' data-id='114'>kami</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='115'>beli</span>? <span class='vocab-word' data-id='116'>Nasi goreng</span>! Dan juga <span class='vocab-word' data-id='117'>air</span>. <span class='vocab-word' data-id='118'>Kami</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='119'>bayar</span> dengan <span class='vocab-word' data-id='120'>uang</span>. Harga tidak <span class='vocab-word' data-id='121'>mahal</span>, sangat <span class='vocab-word' data-id='122'>murah</span>!",
    
    "<span class='vocab-word' data-id='123'>Di</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='124'>sore</span>, <span class='vocab-word' data-id='125'>kami</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='126'>baca</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='127'>majalah</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='128'>musik</span>. Ada <span class='vocab-word' data-id='129'>kabar</span> tentang band <span class='vocab-word' data-id='130'>ternama</span>. <span class='vocab-word' data-id='131'>Mereka</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='132'>akan</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='133'>tampil</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='134'>di</span> Jakarta! <span class='vocab-word' data-id='135'>Kami</span> sangat <span class='vocab-word' data-id='136'>bangga</span> dan excited.",
    
    "\"<span class='vocab-word' data-id='137'>Kita</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='138'>harus</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='139'>pergi</span>!\" kata <span class='vocab-word' data-id='140'>saya</span>. \"<span class='vocab-word' data-id='141'>Ya</span>! <span class='vocab-word' data-id='142'>Kami</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='143'>bisa</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='144'>pergi</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='145'>bersama</span>!\" <span class='vocab-word' data-id='146'>Kami</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='147'>terus</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='148'>tertawa</span>. Ini adalah <span class='vocab-word' data-id='149'>hari</span> yang <span class='vocab-word' data-id='150'>bagus</span>.",
    
    "<span class='vocab-word' data-id='151'>Waktu</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='152'>malam</span>, <span class='vocab-word' data-id='153'>saya</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='154'>pulang</span> ke <span class='vocab-word' data-id='155'>rumah</span>. <span class='vocab-word' data-id='156'>Saya</span> tidak <span class='vocab-word' data-id='157'>lelah</span>. <span class='vocab-word' data-id='158'>Saya</span> sangat <span class='vocab-word' data-id='159'>senang</span>. <span class='vocab-word' data-id='160'>Jantung</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='161'>saya</span> penuh dengan kebahagiaan. \"<span class='vocab-word' data-id='162'>Terima kasih</span>\" <span class='vocab-word' data-id='163'>ku</span> bisikkan.",
    
    "<span class='vocab-word' data-id='164'>Saya</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='165'>masuk</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='166'>kamar</span> dan <span class='vocab-word' data-id='167'>tutup</span> pintu. <span class='vocab-word' data-id='168'>Lalu</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='169'>saya</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='170'>tidur</span>. <span class='vocab-word' data-id='171'>Besok</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='172'>akan</span> ada petualangan <span class='vocab-word' data-id='173'>lagi</span>. <span class='vocab-word' data-id='174'>Tapi</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='175'>sekarang</span>, <span class='vocab-word' data-id='176'>saya</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='177'>ingin</span> <span class='vocab-word' data-id='178'>tidur</span>. <span class='vocab-word' data-id='179'>Selamat malam</span>, Jakarta!"
  ],

